{"type": "article", "id": 13317, "title": "枝形吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-11T06:50:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000240d9tDqOP3TxlsogSk.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这款看上去酷酷的吊灯来自 KEHA3，名为“枝形吊灯”。这些“枝叉”全部是用铝合金管做成的，不规则的样子模仿树枝的分叉。同时，这款灯也是一个隐藏得很“深”的模块化灯具，这里面的每一个分叉其实都可以自由调节，最终可以组成 24 种不同的样式。</span><a href=\"http://keha3.ee/en/indoor-lighting/branch-luhter/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a><span>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000237Yg7mAIUDGwkjPdQ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060002383RTIf65r81GNCEZa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000238nuDzZKRFGSQEOaBx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000239SnBYqJToU0uyxcsM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000239mqINsVUaQulpxbBy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}